    {
      "id": "optimistic_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable entry point into car ownership or a project vehicle with potential? This car is priced to reflect its current condition \u2014 and we believe in full transparency! The vehicle shows significant wear both inside and out, with mechanical issues that will need attention. It's best suited for a handy buyer, a DIY enthusiast, or someone who needs basic transportation on a tight budget. What you see is what you get \u2014 no surprises, just an honest deal at an honest price!",
      "price": 4500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
